Voice-Controlled Calculator 
A desktop application where the user can speak math operations like
"add 45 and 90" or "what is 20 times 3" and the app responds with the correct answer — all using pure Java + Speech APIs.

✅ Features:
Voice input using microphone

Parse natural language commands (e.g., "plus", "times", "divided by")

Speak back the result using text-to-speech

Basic GUI interface (optional)
